
00:02:13,600 --> 00:02:15,360
"Ashes of Love"



00:02:15,400 --> 00:02:17,240
"Episode 37"



00:02:18,270 --> 00:02:19,440
"Qizheng Hall"



00:02:19,440 --> 00:02:20,450
According to Her Majesty’s instructions,



00:02:20,450 --> 00:02:21,020
Your Highness,



00:02:21,260 --> 00:02:22,060
when you’re in mourning,



00:02:22,140 --> 00:02:23,540
you can stay in Xuanji Palace



00:02:23,620 --> 00:02:26,380
and don’t need to go out
to be on night duty for star arrangement.



00:02:28,510 --> 00:02:29,710
Yes.



00:02:29,710 --> 00:02:31,079
Her Majesty shows solicitude for you.



00:02:31,370 --> 00:02:31,940
so we’re specially ordered



00:02:32,110 --> 00:02:34,000
to send you two kinds of different mourning dresses



00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:35,140
for selection.



00:02:38,450 --> 00:02:39,200
Put them down.



00:02:39,940 --> 00:02:40,740
Her Majesty said,



00:02:40,740 --> 00:02:42,340
you can decide



00:02:42,340 --> 00:02:44,970
to choose the one of Heaven Realm
or that of Arowana Family,



00:02:44,970 --> 00:02:47,020
and then we need to take the other one back.



00:02:49,710 --> 00:02:51,220
According to the custom of the Arowana Family,



00:02:51,220 --> 00:02:54,570
I should wear the funeral raw jute clothing
to observe mourning for my mother.



00:02:54,850 --> 00:02:57,140
Her Majesty loves you dearly.



00:02:57,140 --> 00:02:58,220
The raw jute cloth is rough.



00:02:58,280 --> 00:03:00,450
You’re delicate, so you can’t bear it.



00:03:00,450 --> 00:03:03,250
The funeral linen clothing of
Heaven Realm is more suitable.



00:03:13,710 --> 00:03:15,770
You’re supposed to resist against



00:03:16,940 --> 00:03:18,400
the Heavenly Empress and the Bird Family afterwards.



00:03:33,420 --> 00:03:35,600
We have to go back to report to Her Majesty.



00:03:36,220 --> 00:03:37,370
We take our leave.



00:03:53,820 --> 00:03:55,420
Is it a mourning rule in the Heaven Realm



00:03:55,420 --> 00:03:57,650
to throw away the funeral clothing?



00:03:57,940 --> 00:04:00,170
Why is the first Prince angry?



00:04:02,340 --> 00:04:03,820
As ruled in the Heaven Realm,



00:04:04,220 --> 00:04:06,000
one has to wear the funeral linen clothing
when observing mourning,



00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:08,050
but in our family,



00:04:08,050 --> 00:04:10,000
the funeral raw jute clothing should be worn.



00:04:10,680 --> 00:04:13,770
So he made a wrong choice?



00:04:17,540 --> 00:04:18,740
I’m useless.



00:04:22,570 --> 00:04:23,880
Don’t blame yourself.



00:04:24,110 --> 00:04:25,080
Keep filial piety in your heart.



00:04:25,480 --> 00:04:26,800
Your mother knew that.



00:04:27,480 --> 00:04:29,700
It’s very hard for you to observe mourning for her



00:04:29,900 --> 00:04:33,310
under the great pressure from
Heavenly Emperor and Heavenly Empress.



00:04:33,880 --> 00:04:35,540
I believe she would smile in the underworld.



00:04:35,770 --> 00:04:36,740
It’s far from enough.



00:04:39,540 --> 00:04:40,680
I won’t settle down



00:04:42,170 --> 00:04:43,310
if I don’t avenge my mother.



00:04:44,510 --> 00:04:46,380
Why not leave everything behind



00:04:46,820 --> 00:04:49,860
and go away with me and Li?



00:04:50,680 --> 00:04:51,710
Now,



00:04:52,740 --> 00:04:53,380
I’m afraid



00:04:53,380 --> 00:04:57,770
it’s an extravagant hope
to be as unworldly as wild stock.



00:05:03,420 --> 00:05:05,600
What’s your plan in the future?



00:05:06,170 --> 00:05:07,370
No haste, be patient.



00:05:12,850 --> 00:05:14,570
Your mother once asked me



00:05:15,880 --> 00:05:18,220
to give it to you



00:05:18,970 --> 00:05:20,620
if the situation changed.



00:05:21,480 --> 00:05:22,740
What’s in it?



00:05:23,200 --> 00:05:24,510
I have never opened it.



00:05:25,420 --> 00:05:26,450
Check it yourself.



00:05:44,700 --> 00:05:48,740
Force Deployment Map
of the Bird Family on Yimiao Continent



00:05:53,370 --> 00:05:54,620
Your Majesty,



00:05:54,620 --> 00:05:57,420
the first Prince chose the funeral linen clothing.



00:06:00,050 --> 00:06:00,910
You can leave.



00:06:01,310 --> 00:06:02,050
Yes.



00:06:04,850 --> 00:06:06,110
Auntie, you’re a genius.



00:06:06,620 --> 00:06:09,250
You sound Night Immortal out
with the funeral clothing.



00:06:09,770 --> 00:06:10,850
Now you know whether
he follows the Heaven Realm



00:06:10,850 --> 00:06:12,680
or the Arowana Family.



00:06:13,820 --> 00:06:15,420
He is smart,



00:06:15,770 --> 00:06:18,450
loyal and sensible.



00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:20,110
Don’t underestimate him.



00:06:20,970 --> 00:06:22,170
When he was young,



00:06:22,800 --> 00:06:26,000
he scaled himself cruelly



00:06:27,480 --> 00:06:30,280
and dared to take the Fumeng Elixir I gave him.



00:06:31,370 --> 00:06:32,510
He was devastated



00:06:32,680 --> 00:06:34,280
when Su Li died.



00:06:34,800 --> 00:06:37,200
I’m sure that he won’t leave the matter at that.



00:06:38,050 --> 00:06:38,909
But



00:06:38,909 --> 00:06:41,200
he is His Majesty’s son.



00:06:42,340 --> 00:06:44,740
I won’t go too far.



00:06:45,140 --> 00:06:46,170
I just sounded him out



00:06:46,620 --> 00:06:48,800
as a warning.



00:06:49,880 --> 00:06:51,020
Auntie, you’re circumspect and farsighted.



00:06:51,370 --> 00:06:52,800
I must learn from you more.



00:06:57,310 --> 00:06:59,820
It’s the birthday of Moon Immortal today.



00:06:59,820 --> 00:07:02,110
Send my gift to him.



00:07:02,740 --> 00:07:03,820
Yes.



00:07:11,420 --> 00:07:14,540
"House of Marriage"



00:07:20,680 --> 00:07:21,600
Mister Immortal,



00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:23,250
we come to celebrate your birthday.



00:07:23,820 --> 00:07:26,620
May your fortune
be as boundless as the East Sea.



00:07:27,080 --> 00:07:29,200
May you live a long life
as the pine tree in the Southern Mountain.



00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:31,820
The same congratulations.



00:07:32,570 --> 00:07:33,770
Are you blind?



00:07:33,770 --> 00:07:36,340
I’m young



00:07:36,340 --> 00:07:37,710
with delicate features.



00:07:38,170 --> 00:07:40,620
Don’t compare me to the wrinkled old pine tree



00:07:40,620 --> 00:07:41,940
in the Southern Mountain.



00:07:41,940 --> 00:07:43,020
Yes.



00:07:48,510 --> 00:07:49,540
What’s this?



00:07:50,340 --> 00:07:52,450
His Highness is still grounded



00:07:52,450 --> 00:07:55,020
to reflect on his misdeeds in palace today,



00:07:55,020 --> 00:07:57,710
so he ordered us to present the birthday gift.



00:07:57,710 --> 00:07:58,909
You gave an irrelevant answer.



00:07:59,200 --> 00:07:59,880
I asked you what it was,



00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:01,480
but you talked rubbish.



00:08:01,480 --> 00:08:02,680
Forget it. You can leave.



00:08:03,710 --> 00:08:06,570
Mister Immortal, we're leaving.



00:08:18,340 --> 00:08:19,710
It’s a brilliant idea



00:08:19,770 --> 00:08:21,480
to collect those treasures.



00:08:21,600 --> 00:08:22,570
I’m flattered.



00:08:22,970 --> 00:08:24,340
It’s to cater to Moon Immortal’s pleasure.



00:08:24,850 --> 00:08:26,460
Thy are the most fashionable story-telling scripts



00:08:26,460 --> 00:08:27,310
in the Human Realm.



00:08:27,310 --> 00:08:28,800
Moon Immortal



00:08:29,250 --> 00:08:30,740
must be happy.



00:08:31,020 --> 00:08:32,049
I don’t praise you.



00:08:32,510 --> 00:08:34,850
It seems you ignored your
proper occupation in mortal world,



00:08:35,370 --> 00:08:38,280
and always ran irrelevant business
with your fellows.



00:08:38,970 --> 00:08:40,169
If you didn’t hinder me,



00:08:41,140 --> 00:08:42,110
I



00:08:43,820 --> 00:08:46,620
I would have pacified the world



00:08:46,910 --> 00:08:48,110
and created a flourishing age in mortal world.



00:08:48,680 --> 00:08:49,880
Sorry.



00:08:49,880 --> 00:08:51,140
But



00:08:51,420 --> 00:08:52,680
you indeed become smarter



00:08:53,200 --> 00:08:55,020
after the experience in mortal world.



00:08:57,650 --> 00:08:59,140
I’m praising you.



00:09:17,770 --> 00:09:19,020
Mister Immortal.



00:09:20,800 --> 00:09:21,650
Jin Mi,



00:09:22,050 --> 00:09:23,370
here you are.



00:09:23,540 --> 00:09:25,650
Mister Immortal, you make a mistake again.



00:09:25,650 --> 00:09:26,570
I’m not Fairy Jin Mi.



00:09:27,940 --> 00:09:28,850
Kuang Lu.



00:09:29,650 --> 00:09:30,620
What’s up?



00:09:31,310 --> 00:09:33,480
Why do you get a nosebleed?



00:09:35,250 --> 00:09:36,280
I get inflamed.



00:09:36,280 --> 00:09:37,250
Come.



00:09:37,250 --> 00:09:38,110
Xu Feng



00:09:38,110 --> 00:09:40,450
sent a box of pornographic scripts.



00:09:40,450 --> 00:09:41,650
They’re new.



00:09:42,050 --> 00:09:44,110
Let’s read them together.



00:09:44,450 --> 00:09:45,020
Well,



00:09:45,370 --> 00:09:47,370
I come to you for something else.



00:09:47,370 --> 00:09:50,000
His Highness can’t go out
as he is observing mourning for his mother,



00:09:50,620 --> 00:09:52,510
so he ordered me to come
to celebrate your birthday.



00:09:54,000 --> 00:09:56,800
May you be young forever.



00:09:56,800 --> 00:09:58,510
You’re clever.



00:10:05,710 --> 00:10:07,140
It’s a good thing.



00:10:08,220 --> 00:10:09,420
It’s shining.



00:10:09,420 --> 00:10:10,740
With it,



00:10:10,740 --> 00:10:11,770
I can read the scripts



00:10:11,770 --> 00:10:14,450
Xu Feng sent at night.



00:10:15,020 --> 00:10:16,170
Wonderful.



00:10:17,770 --> 00:10:19,600
Run Yu is poor.



00:10:20,910 --> 00:10:22,220
Give him my thanks



00:10:22,280 --> 00:10:23,880
and consolations.



00:10:24,850 --> 00:10:25,880
I will.



00:10:25,880 --> 00:10:27,140
Thank you, Mister Immortal.



00:10:27,820 --> 00:10:28,510
Well,



00:10:28,510 --> 00:10:30,510
Run Yu can’t attend my birthday banquet.



00:10:30,510 --> 00:10:31,770
Kuang Lu, come.



00:10:31,770 --> 00:10:33,600
Let’s drink and enjoy ourselves.



00:10:34,800 --> 00:10:36,450
I’m a low-level fairy.



00:10:36,910 --> 00:10:38,000
I’m afraid…



00:10:38,450 --> 00:10:40,850
Water Immortal will bring Jin Mi.



00:10:40,850 --> 00:10:42,850
Ask your father to bring you.



00:10:43,310 --> 00:10:44,510
Or,



00:10:44,510 --> 00:10:47,710
I’ll be lonely at the banquet.



00:10:47,710 --> 00:10:49,250
I’m unhappy.



00:10:49,710 --> 00:10:51,080
Then I’ll come.



00:10:51,820 --> 00:10:52,910
Thank you, Mister Immortal.



00:10:53,480 --> 00:10:55,250
Good girl.



00:10:55,250 --> 00:10:57,200
I’m taking my leave now.



00:10:57,540 --> 00:10:58,400
Okay.



00:11:12,110 --> 00:11:13,650
Wind Immortal, Water Immortal,



00:11:13,880 --> 00:11:16,050
Immortal Jin Mi come.



00:11:16,570 --> 00:11:17,940
Amazing.



00:11:18,400 --> 00:11:19,200
Water Immortal.



00:11:19,200 --> 00:11:20,340
Jin Mi.



00:11:22,170 --> 00:11:23,310
Come on.



00:11:23,310 --> 00:11:25,540
Help yourselves.



00:11:25,540 --> 00:11:26,850
Don’t stand on ceremony. Come on.



00:11:26,850 --> 00:11:28,140
Make yourselves at home.



00:11:28,180 --> 00:11:29,060
Eat whatever you like.



00:11:31,600 --> 00:11:33,420
Do you know what my gift is?



00:11:33,420 --> 00:11:34,400
What is it?



00:11:34,400 --> 00:11:36,000
Something from the mortal world.



00:11:36,000 --> 00:11:37,080
Try it.



00:11:39,310 --> 00:11:40,910
So clear!



00:11:42,000 --> 00:11:44,180
I can see things more clearly.



00:11:44,820 --> 00:11:45,580
Do you like it?



00:11:45,880 --> 00:11:46,620
Wonderful.



00:11:47,100 --> 00:11:48,680
With this treasure,



00:11:48,680 --> 00:11:51,140
I can read 100 scripts in a day.



00:11:54,280 --> 00:11:55,200
Jin Mi,



00:11:55,770 --> 00:11:59,820
it turns out that you’re
more beautiful than what I imagined.



00:12:00,510 --> 00:12:02,050
Princess Sui He comes.



00:12:02,050 --> 00:12:04,110
Fairy Yuan Ji comes.



00:12:06,000 --> 00:12:06,740
Mister Immortal,



00:12:06,740 --> 00:12:08,000
I come on behalf of Her Majesty.



00:12:08,000 --> 00:12:09,020
Okay. Good girl, help yourself.



00:12:09,480 --> 00:12:11,370
Yuan Ji. Yuan Ji.



00:12:19,250 --> 00:12:20,970
Good girl. I don’t want to eat it.



00:12:33,020 --> 00:12:34,340
Yuan Ji,



00:12:34,340 --> 00:12:35,710
you’re so stingy.



00:12:36,170 --> 00:12:38,570
You come without bringing a gift.



00:12:38,570 --> 00:12:40,620
I was thinking



00:12:40,620 --> 00:12:42,280
how to continue the
second life of the white snake



00:12:42,280 --> 00:12:45,250
after the collapse of
Leifeng Pagoda these days.



00:12:45,600 --> 00:12:46,970
I wanted to



00:12:46,970 --> 00:12:49,080
make her a fruit elf in the Floral Realm,



00:12:49,370 --> 00:12:52,850
and you could decide
her destiny and marriage.



00:12:53,200 --> 00:12:54,620
But it seems that



00:12:54,620 --> 00:12:56,220
you don’t like my gift.



00:12:58,740 --> 00:12:59,420
Yuan Ji,



00:12:59,770 --> 00:13:02,280
I know you care about me.



00:13:02,510 --> 00:13:03,250
It’s



00:13:03,250 --> 00:13:05,710
an excellent gift.



00:13:05,710 --> 00:13:07,250
Go. Let’s drink.



00:13:07,250 --> 00:13:07,880
Go.



00:13:11,200 --> 00:13:12,340
Eat it.



00:13:12,340 --> 00:13:14,680
Thank you, Daddy.



00:13:16,170 --> 00:13:18,110
I still think it’s unusual.



00:13:18,510 --> 00:13:19,770
I feel the same way.



00:13:20,280 --> 00:13:21,310
Jin Mi.



00:13:23,140 --> 00:13:25,940
It has to be talked about at length.



00:13:26,340 --> 00:13:26,740
By then…



00:13:26,740 --> 00:13:27,310
Daddy.



00:13:29,620 --> 00:13:30,450
Go.



00:13:49,420 --> 00:13:50,570
Besides me,



00:13:51,140 --> 00:13:52,510
do you like Xu Feng?



00:13:54,400 --> 00:13:55,200
Yes.



00:13:55,200 --> 00:13:56,570
How about Moon Immortal?



00:13:56,910 --> 00:13:57,940
Yes.



00:13:58,170 --> 00:13:59,370
And Lord Yan You?



00:13:59,820 --> 00:14:01,020
Yes.



00:14:01,880 --> 00:14:03,940
If Jin Mi is a piece of barren land,



00:14:03,940 --> 00:14:06,740
no matter what seed is sowed
and what fertilizer is applied,



00:14:06,740 --> 00:14:08,620
no matter how you water it
with the utmost care,



00:14:08,620 --> 00:14:11,080
it won’t blossom in return.



00:14:11,310 --> 00:14:13,940
Falling in love with her
is like a stone dropped into the sea.



00:14:13,940 --> 00:14:15,080
There will be no respond from her.



00:14:15,080 --> 00:14:16,680
It takes time and energy.



00:14:17,370 --> 00:14:18,340
Are you afraid?



00:14:18,970 --> 00:14:20,510
Jin Mi is essentially a good girl,



00:14:20,910 --> 00:14:24,170
but she is cold and heartless from childhood.



00:14:24,400 --> 00:14:26,000
She doesn’t like anyone,



00:14:26,800 --> 00:14:30,110
not to mention love.



00:14:33,480 --> 00:14:34,740
She used to be cold,



00:14:35,370 --> 00:14:37,710
passionate but ruthless.



00:14:39,200 --> 00:14:40,620
Now she is heartless but single-minded.



00:14:42,280 --> 00:14:43,020
Why does she



00:14:43,540 --> 00:14:46,000
change so dramatically?



00:14:46,450 --> 00:14:48,400
I took Floating Dream Pill before,



00:14:49,420 --> 00:14:52,170
so I forgot my mother and childhood memory.



00:14:53,650 --> 00:14:57,880
Is Mi controlled?



00:15:02,280 --> 00:15:03,650
Mi,



00:15:04,110 --> 00:15:05,710
which one is the real you?



00:15:14,000 --> 00:15:15,420
Yun Elixir?



00:15:22,220 --> 00:15:24,510
His Majesty comes.



00:15:26,970 --> 00:15:28,740
Your Majesty, welcome.



00:15:29,140 --> 00:15:30,220
Your Majesty, welcome.



00:15:30,510 --> 00:15:31,480
Your Majesty, welcome.



00:15:31,940 --> 00:15:32,970
Don’t stand on ceremony.



00:15:32,970 --> 00:15:35,080
It’s the birthday banquet
of Moon Immortal today.



00:15:35,600 --> 00:15:36,510
Make yourselves at home.



00:15:36,510 --> 00:15:38,620
Your Majesty, you have to
deal with a host of problems every day.



00:15:38,850 --> 00:15:41,200
Why brings you here today?



00:15:41,200 --> 00:15:44,800
Moon Immortal, do you blame me
for coming without being invited



00:15:44,800 --> 00:15:46,800
or complain I haven’t come for long?



00:15:46,800 --> 00:15:48,110
Not at all.



00:15:48,110 --> 00:15:50,340
My humble house is honored by your presence.



00:15:51,880 --> 00:15:53,020
Our family members have come.



00:15:53,420 --> 00:15:54,400
There are not many people,



00:15:55,600 --> 00:15:57,540
so it’s sort of deserted.



00:15:58,170 --> 00:15:59,310
My Eight Characters are unlucky.



00:16:00,110 --> 00:16:01,200
During my birthday banquet,



00:16:01,200 --> 00:16:02,970
the first Prince is observing
mourning for his mother,



00:16:02,970 --> 00:16:04,340
while the second Prince is grounded...



00:16:04,340 --> 00:16:06,340
You want me to release them?



00:16:07,600 --> 00:16:09,650
Forget them.



00:16:10,170 --> 00:16:12,050
Let’s enjoy ourselves.



00:16:13,310 --> 00:16:15,080
Immortal Tai Si is here.



00:16:15,480 --> 00:16:17,880
You know many novel poems.



00:16:18,170 --> 00:16:20,450
It's a good idea to take it as an entertainment.



00:16:21,250 --> 00:16:22,800
Okay. Your Majesty,



00:16:23,250 --> 00:16:26,110
I learned a poem in mortal world recently.



00:16:26,510 --> 00:16:27,740
I’ll entertain



00:16:27,740 --> 00:16:32,400
you and everyone here.



00:16:32,910 --> 00:16:33,310
Please.



00:16:33,310 --> 00:16:34,050
Let’s enjoy it.



00:16:43,600 --> 00:16:47,310
Don’t you see Lord Xu’s two sons
who were born utterly remarkable?



00:16:47,310 --> 00:16:49,650
The duo came one after another
following an auspicious dream.



00:16:49,650 --> 00:16:52,170
Confucius and the Buddha
personally brought them in their arms.



00:16:52,170 --> 00:16:54,680
Both are from the heaven, unicorn foals.



00:16:54,680 --> 00:16:57,310
The elder is nine years old,
he is clever and pure.



00:16:57,310 --> 00:16:59,770
Autumn waters are his soul,
jade is his bones.



00:16:59,770 --> 00:17:02,510
The younger son is five years old,
exhibiting an imposing presence.



00:17:02,510 --> 00:17:05,020
The guests that fill the hall
all turn their heads.



00:17:05,079 --> 00:17:07,540
