00:34:45,940 --> 00:34:47,770
Love me a little bit more every day.



00:34:49,310 --> 00:34:51,310
Day after day,



00:34:51,940 --> 00:34:53,710
month after month



00:34:55,199 --> 00:34:57,370
and year after year.



00:34:59,710 --> 00:35:01,140
