I hope your love lasts forever.



00:35:07,650 --> 00:35:09,250
Will you?



00:35:13,480 --> 00:35:14,570
It’s late at night.



00:35:14,970 --> 00:35:16,110
I have to go back.



00:36:19,200 --> 00:36:20,620
It really cracks.



00:36:23,250 --> 00:36:24,400
Mi,



00:36:26,910 --> 00:36:28,970
you treat Xu Feng without reservation.



00:36:31,420 --> 00:36:32,570
You know what,



00:36:33,770 --> 00:36:36,510
when I saw the dream
shown by the Beast of Dreams



00:36:38,280 --> 00:36:40,340
and you kissed each other,



00:37:04,680 --> 00:37:06,910
do you know how sad I was?



00:37:10,220 --> 00:37:11,820
I wish



00:37:12,450 --> 00:37:14,280
you didn’t know what love was,



00:37:16,050 --> 00:37:17,770
wouldn’t fall in love,



00:37:19,370 --> 00:37:20,740
couldn’t love anyone



00:37:21,820 --> 00:37:23,650
or be in love.



00:38:06,340 --> 00:38:10,620
I have nothing left.



00:38:13,710 --> 00:38:14,910
I only have you.



00:38:17,370 --> 00:38:18,910
Don’t leave me,



00:38:19,940 --> 00:38:20,740
okay?



00:39:39,080 --> 00:39:41,310
Frost Flower, why do you ignore me?



00:39:43,820 --> 00:39:45,940
Don’t you want to go out?



00:41:33,880 --> 00:41:35,080
Liu Ying



00:41:35,650 --> 00:41:37,140
Jin Mi, please do me a favor.


